Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:28.52,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.06,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我下这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.11,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:32.79,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\3c&HD554E9&\bord2\fad(331,200)\pos(305,379)}真唯 真可惜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:32.64,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也吃不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.33,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优希来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:36.02,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
